{"word":"ἐπίκειμαι","slug":"ἐπίκειμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπίϰειμαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κεῖμαι\">κεῖμαι</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘lie in superimposed position’, <b>lie over <a href='B:500 11:38'>J 11:38</a>; <a href='B:500 21:9'>21:9</a>.</b> In imagery of stormy weather <b>hover <a href='B:510 27:20'>Ac 27:20</a>;</b> of obligatory cultic tradition <b>impose <a href='B:650 9:10'>Hb 9:10</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘apply pressure’, <b>press,</b> of a crowd <b><a href='B:490 5:1'>Lk 5:1</a>;</b> of public outcry <b><a href='B:490 23:23'>23:23</a>;</b> of circumstance <b><a href='B:530 9:16'>1 Cor 9:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπικατάρατος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπικέκλημαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}